  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1607720/extras/e68baa656aa1643fce282b6988dc3cad.poster.avif?t=1736883724\" width=600 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1607720/extras/e68baa656aa1643fce282b6988dc3cad.webm?t=1736883724\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1607720/extras/e68baa656aa1643fce282b6988dc3cad.mp4?t=1736883724\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rimebeard is a grid-based <strong>puzzlegame</strong> where you <strong>create</strong>, <strong>remove</strong> and <strong>push</strong> blocks of ice strategically to <strong>extinguish all flames</strong> in each level. Navigate through the level methodically and use various other elements such as rocks, crates, pipes and more to achieve your goal and avoid getting stuck between a flame and a hard place. Over 70 levels are waiting to be solved in this sokoban-style game based on a NES classic. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1607720/extras/975dfa1eb77f265e19eefe5e9bc4357e.poster.avif?t=1736883724\" width=600 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1607720/extras/975dfa1eb77f265e19eefe5e9bc4357e.webm?t=1736883724\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1607720/extras/975dfa1eb77f265e19eefe5e9bc4357e.mp4?t=1736883724\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1607720/extras/e68baa656aa1643fce282b6988dc3cad.poster.avif?t=1736883724\" width=600 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1607720/extras/e68baa656aa1643fce282b6988dc3cad.webm?t=1736883724\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1607720/extras/e68baa656aa1643fce282b6988dc3cad.mp4?t=1736883724\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rimebeard is a grid-based <strong>puzzlegame</strong> where you <strong>create</strong>, <strong>remove</strong> and <strong>push</strong> blocks of ice strategically to <strong>extinguish all flames</strong> in each level. Navigate through the level methodically and use various other elements such as rocks, crates, pipes and more to achieve your goal and avoid getting stuck between a flame and a hard place. Over 70 levels are waiting to be solved in this sokoban-style game based on a NES classic. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1607720/extras/975dfa1eb77f265e19eefe5e9bc4357e.poster.avif?t=1736883724\" width=600 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1607720/extras/975dfa1eb77f265e19eefe5e9bc4357e.webm?t=1736883724\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1607720/extras/975dfa1eb77f265e19eefe5e9bc4357e.mp4?t=1736883724\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
